on damage of player:
    attacker is a player
    set {pvp.enemy.%victim%} to attacker's name
    set {pvp.enemy.%attacker%} to victim's name
    send "&l&cPvP&r &8»&c You have been attacked by &e%attacker%&c! Do not log off!" to victim
    send "&l&cPvP&r &8»&c You attacked &e%victim%&c! Do not log off!" to attacker
